### Login user
POST http://0.0.0.0:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "heheuser",
  "password": "testpass"
}

### Register user
POST http://0.0.0.0:8000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "hh",
  "last_name": "hfh",
  "email": "hehe@gmail.com",
  "username": "heheuser",
  "password": "testpass",
  "role": "Candidate"
}

